OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778523070
OL,3,CPM announces plans to nationalise
OL,4,CBritish Steel
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has announced powers
OL,7,Fto fully nationalise British Steel
OL,8,Fafter efforts to secure a commercial
OL,9,Fdeal for its sale failed.
OL,11,FReports at the weekend had suggested
OL,12,Fan announcement would be made in the
OL,13,Fking's speech on Wednesday.
OL,15,FSpeaking to media in the wake of
OL,16,FLabour's sweeping local election
OL,17,Flosses last week, the Prime Minister
OL,18,Fsaid legislation would be brought
OL,19,Fforward this week to take "full
OL,20,Fnational ownership" of the company for
OL,21,Fthe first time since 1988.
OL,26,@{D@[OU
