CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778523070
OL,3,CPM announces plans to nationalise
OL,4,CBritish Steel
OL,6,FHe said: "In Scunthorpe, we've been
OL,7,Fnegotiating with the current owner,
OL,8,Fand a commercial sale has not been
OL,9,Fpossible, and now a public interest
OL,10,Ftest could be met.
OL,12,F"So, I can announce that legislation
OL,13,Fwill be brought forward this week to
OL,14,Fgive the government powers, subject to
OL,15,Fthat public interest test, to take
OL,16,Ffull national ownership of British
OL,17,FSteel."
OL,26,@nD@JOUtD@AOUyD@GO]
