OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778523070
OL,3,CPM announces plans to nationalise
OL,4,CBritish Steel
OL,6,FThe announcement comes a year after
OL,7,Fthe government took over the daily
OL,8,Frunning of the business from its
OL,9,FChinese owner Jingye.
OL,11,FMinisters passed an emergency law to
OL,12,Ftake control amid concerns Jingye
OL,13,Fplanned to close Scunthorpe's blast
OL,14,Ffurnaces.
OL,16,FJingye bosses said the site, which
OL,17,Femploys 3,500 people, was losing
OL,18,F#700,000 day and was no longer
OL,19,Ffinancially viable.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
