OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778523070
OL,3,CPM announces plans to nationalise
OL,4,CBritish Steel
OL,6,FIt is not the first time the
OL,7,Fgovernment has intervened in British
OL,8,FSteel. The Insolvency Service took
OL,9,Fover its running for nine months after
OL,10,Fit collapsed in 2019.
OL,12,FBusiness Secretary Peter Kyle said:
OL,13,F"Strong domestic steel production is
OL,14,Fvital for our economy, and this
OL,15,Flegislation would allow us to ensure
OL,16,Fstability for British Steel's workers,
OL,17,Fsuppliers and customers and avoid
OL,18,Fdamaging disruption to crucial supply
OL,19,Fchains, while we consider options for
OL,20,Fthe site's future."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
