FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1778523070
OL,3,CPM announces plans to nationalise
OL,4,CBritish Steel
OL,6,FUK Steel, the trade association for
OL,7,Fthe industry, welcomed the
OL,8,Fannouncement.
OL,10,FDirector general Gareth Stace said:
OL,11,F"This provides vital certainty for the
OL,12,Fworkforce, the company's customers and
OL,13,Fthe wider supply chain at a critical
OL,14,Fmoment.
OL,16,F"Steel is a foundation industry and a
OL,17,Frecognised strategic national asset.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
